{"tid":2020303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始稱本港需要思考如何迎接病毒存在的新常態","createTime":"2020-05-17T03:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T04:02:12.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"257f9ab883eb692d2581064d58128e97df9c6814","tid":2020303,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:19:23.000Z","msg":"陳肇始稱本港需要思考如何迎接病毒存在的新常態<br />\n2020-05-17 HKT 08:43<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始出席一個電台節目時表示，根據世衛及專家看法，新型冠狀病毒可能一直存在，本港需要思考如何迎接新常態，市民或要常戴口罩及帶搓手液等。<br />\n<br />\n至於何時可以再放寬社交距離等措施，陳肇始說，需要「張弛有度」並評估風險，近日出現新的確診個案，有待衞生防護中心追蹤感染源頭後，再評估情況。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又說，會擴大病毒檢測量，當局會主動向在機場工作、以及在護老院與殘疾院舍內工作人士，取樣本檢測。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526626-20200517.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526626-20200517.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=419f0270\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1526626-20200517.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0705d7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1526626-20200517.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我認為新常態應該係:<br />\n市民做好防禦措施後如常生活<br />\n政府應取消所有社交距離等措施以振興疲弱的經濟，以及豁免從疫情受控國家(如泰國)回港需隔離的規定</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"ee49e0f81f1e2fd0d2dd056627e0626f83b65e43","tid":2020303,"uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:32:54.000Z","msg":"想永續限聚令又想人黎使錢<br />\n又唔想人專消費黃店者<br />\n港共"},{"pid":"da76dd4cb081eed1bedab19869adb03ca7a482de","tid":2020303,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:35:42.000Z","msg":"繼續用警察打壓市民咪得囉<br />\n2人限聚令啦"},{"pid":"bbb5f2a9f1615ac9acfbb0de1865fecd0dad21c2","tid":2020303,"uid":248299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T03:37:49.000Z","msg":"新常態<br />\n支那term<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b8334466de59d2c695b8e110186abb166e5c08a","tid":2020303,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"幫大陸放風預備開闗一齊死?"}]}